  "sections": {
    "gp_section_625369882908688947": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "de385a5a42ab099c40c2a7c8919afcde7f760c9e3a12971f99e2bf73132c60ac_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-oS0OaV7f_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg-tUtWxKhh_text": "<p>Liam H.</p>",
        "gg1n7ZOO0-b_text": "<p>Details:</p>",
        "gg1o0gkxDYu_text": "<p>As an avid runner&nbsp;</p>",
        "gg3NKTpOzbt_text": "<p>We believe in hassle-free shopping. That’s why Boxhero Bamboo Boxer Shorts come with <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns and exchanges.</strong></span>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If they don’t fit just right or you’re not completely satisfied, simply return or exchange them at no cost to you. Enjoy comfort without any risk.</p>",
        "gg3xLhRxEhT_text": "<p>32-33</p>",
        "gg4e1Pb0NWx_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-b179c129-a2aa-441e-85d1-6b14dfe85d5b.svg",
        "gg5g09zhY8N_text": "<p>Absolutely the most comfortable underwear I’ve ever bought. They fit perfectly, stay in place, and feel like a second skin.</p>",
        "gg5omjG4FTY_text": "<p>Our innovative Bamboo Powered BoxHero™ Fabrics boasts a buttery soft feel with ultimate stretch, support and breathability, making it one of our most-loved and sold out boxers of all times.</p>",
        "gg5qyYTYLNz_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "gg6FyGa3apR_text": "<p>30-31</p>",
        "gg6_EEbztta_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gg8vkzyRom3_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-f2ab390a-662e-4a0e-bf4c-237bc7b9d578.svg",
        "gg9djR-c3ZU_childItem_0": "<p>reviews</p>",
        "gg9h1exo3hm_text": "<p>81-84</p>",
        "ggAEVbUSJBl_text": "<p>Marc C.</p>",
        "ggAGzVndjra_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggAXiE1gSor_text": "<p>2XL</p>",
        "ggB0brh0_Fp_text": "<p>STRETCH</p>",
        "ggD_fPnY0sn_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_0": "<p>Why You&#039;ll Love It &nbsp;</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_1": "<p>Size &amp; Fit</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_2": "<p>Fabrics &amp; Care</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_3": "<p>45 Day Perfect Fit Money Guarantee</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_4": "<p>Anti-Hole Guarantee</p>",
        "ggEHgpqPnHj_childItem_5": "<p>Free Returns &amp; Exchanges</p>",
        "ggFJhv6XtFa_text": "<p>Camelia J.</p>",
        "ggHxm-K0LAX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggIWSuErOmh_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-99e68524-3c41-4592-84e6-89ad5a5ced24.svg",
        "ggJai-mIzBo_text": "<p>Avery N.</p>",
        "ggLbdEuXnjp_text": "<p>Rated <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong>4.6</strong></span>/ 5 based on <span style=\"color:#00B67A;\"><strong><u>3800+ Customers.</u></strong></span></p>",
        "ggLi9e3uAk2_text": "<p>Olivier J.</p>",
        "ggMOFdfwuZp_text": "<p>BoxHero Bamboo Boxer Shorts are crafted from ultra-stretchy bamboo fabric, making them 83% more durable than conventional boxers. Designed for ultimate breathability, they neutralize odors and wick away moisture, keeping you fresh, comfortable, and confident all day long – no matter where life takes you</p>",
        "ggMXtYiLE4i_text": "<p>UNREAL comfort</p>",
        "ggMh8UP1KeW_text": "<p>Satisfied beyond belief!!!!&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggNfcoKkxKB_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggONRFY2ZJc_text": "<ul><li><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>No-Roll Waistband</strong></span> that won't pinch or bunch</li><li><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Hypoallergenic</strong></span> skin-safe fabric&nbsp;</li><li><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Anti-odor</strong></span> BambooFiber™ Technology</li><li>HeroMesh™ <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>360° Cooling Zones</strong></span></li><li>Supportive <span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Contour Pouch&nbsp;</strong></span></li><li><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong>Pre-Shrunk</strong></span> to avoid laundry shrinking</li></ul>",
        "ggRSQR38XsP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggS3SEZqTgt_text": "<p><strong>Got a hole in your boxer?</strong> No problem! If your boxer develops a tear <span style=\"background-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);color:#00237E;\"><strong>within 6 months,</strong></span> send it back to us and we’ll replace it for free. BoxHero is built to last, and we stand by our commitment to quality.</p>",
        "ggS4J8xidtx_text": "<p>SOFTNESS</p>",
        "ggSG-PVMSvO_text": "<p>34-37</p>",
        "ggSV8qjUIF1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggTkLsyPB4F_text": "<p>38-43</p>",
        "ggTtlCbl8iP_text": "<p>WEIGHT</p>",
        "ggWSJUxnYcX_text": "<p>The most comfortable…&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggY2hH_XtMS_text": "<ul><li><strong>Boxhero Bamboo Boxer Shorts</strong> <span style=\"color:#313131;\">have a snug, supportive fit, designed to stay in place throughout the day.</span></li><li><strong>Take your normal size</strong> <span style=\"color:#313131;\">in boxer briefs.</span></li></ul>",
        "ggY4PV1YwiP_text": "<p>We’re confident in our quality, so we offer a <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-Day Guarantee</strong></span>. Try them, and if they don’t fit or feel right, just email us for a new pair or a full refund—no questions asked.</p>",
        "ggYGs69FCaJ_text": "<p>85-93</p>",
        "ggYcGmaU_82_text": "<p>About our guarantee</p>",
        "ggYsr3DLl0H_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>Waist</strong></span></p><p>cm</p>",
        "ggZ5ZjGQGbG_text": "<p>These boxers are like a hug—soft, supportive, and luxurious. They stay in place all day, even after multiple washes.&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggZPjVhekCZ_text": "<p><strong>Customer Email:</strong> info@boxhero.co</p>",
        "gg_SGag8dAL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-8432f01a-70e3-413e-b123-425198d89541.svg",
        "gg_q4SQCEgL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "ggaAE89r1UW_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands but..</p>",
        "ggaFfzg8CK6_text": "<p>94-105</p>",
        "ggcrnmF_lIE_text": "<p>I’ve tried many brands, but these boxers are on a whole different level. They’re incredibly soft, supportive, and durable.</p>",
        "ggd3JoQWjf4_text": "<p>105+</p>",
        "ggdBeG9LSOZ_text": "<p>My partner says they’re the most comfortable he’s ever worn. After multiple washes, they keep their shape and softness.</p>",
        "ggeFgXsgSFe_text": "<p>XL</p>",
        "ggeR4bUufTV_text": "<p>M</p>",
        "ggeny5F_KBU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-e25e8df1-6b91-476e-b7ae-ca524fc71994.svg",
        "gghJgaCYjNP_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>Waist</strong></span></p><p>in</p>",
        "gghO-CfoMnU_text": "<p>No odor or sweat, this bamboo really works!</p>",
        "ggiBPVdR7g-_text": "<p>As a runner, finding the right underwear is crucial. These offer excellent support and breathability. They keep me dry and comfortable</p>",
        "ggiCWw-UEx6_text": "<p>Jason K.</p>",
        "ggkEmYBp-0H_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>PRO TIP:</strong></span> If you’re in between sizes or prefer a looser fit, consider sizing up</p>",
        "ggke2kdjjPM_text": "<p>Did you know ?</p>",
        "ggmzpfLufmi_text": "<p>43+</p>",
        "ggo8ElaZcig_text": "<p>76-78</p>",
        "ggpTskvks_G_text": "<p>Two weeks of walking around Europe, constantly adjusting and sweating. After switching to Boxhero, the comfort blew me away. 100% satisfied!</p>",
        "ggqhBhWDBtQ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-3668000f-9259-4130-90bc-90b334c37ec7.png",
        "ggrzqZGt_jj_text": "<p>S</p>",
        "ggsTCZ-Um--_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>Bamboo</strong></span> is one of the <span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>strongest and most durable</strong></span> natural fibers, which is why we chose it for our Boxhero Boxer Shorts.</p>",
        "ggs_s6lEDOC_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggvTGprVUnW_text": "<p>L</p>",
        "ggwn-GKtqmn_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-b179c129-a2aa-441e-85d1-6b14dfe85d5b.svg",
