    "gp_section_625369882925466163": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9a5460415ec433dbbc15cf9ebd4d20b4ce04fd53edd4d5753a43a5dea93f4d5f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggQ0Wtpv_Ah_label": "<p>TRY IT RISK-FREE – TODAY AT 50% OFF!</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p>What is bamboo fibre and why is it used for boxer shorts?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p>Why do dermatologists recommend bamboo fibre boxers?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p>How does the breathability of bamboo fibre boxers differ from other materials?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p>What does the “buy 2 + 3 free” offer mean?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_4": "<p>How does the durability of bamboo fibre boxers compare to traditional boxers?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_5": "<p>Are bamboo fibre boxers suitable for sensitive skin?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_6": "<p>Can I wash bamboo fibre boxers in the washing machine?&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggRO0x1JBf5_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre is a natural material that’s increasingly appreciated for its soft, breathable, and environmentally friendly properties. It’s used in the manufacture of our boxer shorts to provide optimal comfort and promote better intimate hygiene.</p>",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "FAQ",
        "ggXHYiMjwOM_text": "<p>Dermatologists recommend our bamboo fibre boxers because of their softness and their ability to reduce unpleasant friction, helping to maintain impeccable hygiene in intimate areas.</p>",
        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>The exceptional breathability of our bamboo fibre boxers allows air to circulate, reducing humidity and perspiration. You will always feel comfortable and fresh, whatever your activity.</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p>Bamboo fibre boxer shorts are designed for added durability thanks to their high-quality material. They are more resistant to wear and last longer than regular boxers.</p>",
        "ggkYAJ7acNt_text": "<p>Yes, our bamboo fibre boxers are machine-washable. Please follow the care instructions included with your boxers for best washing practices.</p>",
        "ggmkvDRWsjL_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-day</strong></span> money&nbsp;-back guarantee</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>Yes, in general, bamboo fibre boxers are suitable for sensitive skin due to their softness and ability to reduce skin irritation. However, if you have specific concerns, we recommend consulting a healthcare professional.</p>",
        "ggrxGymrlkU_text": "<p>Our special offer allows you to buy 2 bamboo fibre boxer shorts and receive 3 free. This is a limited opportunity to renew your collection of high-quality underwear. Not to be missed!</p>",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p>Still have questions ? Check here</p>",
        "ggxet32tdWW_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns</strong></span><strong>,</strong> NO QUESTIONS ASKED&nbsp;</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-625369882925466163"
    },
