        "ggW6i3PixrQ_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">Finally boxer shorts That don't rip... and smell GOOD!</span>",
        "ggWYmWxn-eN_text": "<p>The fabric of BoxHero is so soft, I no longer deal with that irritating rubbing I used to get from other brands that cost me 2x more. Plus, they stay fresh all day—10/10 for comfort and durability!</p>",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-ab728eca-73f8-494e-a092-8eb595a9c948.jpg",
        "ggWe6XmJzW1_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Capture_d_ecran_2025-03-31_a_09.39.51.png",
        "ggWpEm7o-W0_text": "<p>'m a big guy, and these fit great. No riding up—they stay in place. They feel amazing, and there's no chafing, even on heavy workdays. This is my second set, and the first still looks and feels the same after six months. I'm replacing all my old boxers with BoxHero Bamboo boxers.</p>",
        "ggXodWLXYj9_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "gga14oHm6kL_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">wife approves, and i love them&nbsp;</span>",
        "gga1VaOr4fd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/Template_Avis_Cadre_Photo_1.png",
        "ggaIIux6kpV_text": "<p>I have tried so many different underwear, just to throw them away. These I like. The size is good, material is good, waist band is good, pouch is good, and they are holding up well. They have not faded, the waist band has not lost any strength, and they seem to work perfect. I am giving them a five stars because they fit and feel good wearing, and they look good too.</p>",
        "ggaplnOalc2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0825/9813/4039/files/gempages_491320059759690869-c787c8d9-660e-47cf-a44b-e4d573d9168a.jpg",
        "ggbH-IVQ7BE_text": "<p>4.8/5 based on 3438 reviews</p>",
        "ggbNlt912uz_text": "<span style=\"color:#09090A;\">The size is good, material is good, waist band is good</span>",
        "ggcmHQakp1d_text": "<p>I've bought the Boxhero, which has a natural soft and comfortable feel and does an excellent job of wicking moisture. These are the most comfortable ones I have ever worn!</p>",
        "gghbdWf1S0I_text": "<p>Tommy G.</p>",
        "ggiUNvvbYkT_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggj55v5oBWj_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">I’m a big guy, and these stay put!</span>",
        "ggjmKYCRCBG_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggku5Q9ZIvW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0703/7363/8402/files/17_85d6016f-94c1-4ff7-a959-2a48bfc513ff.jpg",
        "gglsj97MMsI_text": "Happy Customers",
        "ggmAceQtFS9_text": "50,481+",
        "ggoFT06VXY4_text": "<p>The breathability of these shorts is simply exceptional. No matter what I’m doing, I always feel comfortable and fresh. Bamboo really does make all the difference—honestly, these are life-changing. Plus, my wife approves, and I love them!</p>",
        "ggpcGRoEQhT_text": "<p>After a full day of work, there's no sweat or odor. I feel fresh from morning till night—best pair I've ever owned, and I wish I had bought these earlier in my life. I will definitely be ordering 5 more pairs in the next few months.</p>",
        "ggqtOcmPD1Q_childItem_0": "<p>verified buyer</p>",
        "ggsa-JkQbqv_text": "<p>Alex N.</p>",
        "ggtXh0XHscb_text": "ultra soft, i need 20 more pairs!",
        "ggtb5aRMmlI_text": "<span style=\"color:#000000;\">all day comfort and no moisture</span>",
        "gguY7QvohhM_text": "<p>ron d.</p>",
        "ggvOiRjsRSc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://boxhero.co/cdn/shop/files/gempages_491320059759690869-99c7d589-1f15-4fb4-908a-747d39743ceb.jpg?v=11217554910590163594",
        "ggxQbXj5HuA_text": "<p>Jeff C.</p>",
        "ggyX7DdMLJ__text": "<p>My husband was fed up with uncomfortable underwear that didn’t last. After switching to BoxHero, he’s thrilled with how soft and comfortable they are—even after multiple washes. And the best part? No more sagging or fading! And honestly, I love how good he looks in them.</p>"
      },
